  "text": "5th May, 2005 Notification No.37/2005-NT-Customs In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (2) of section 9AA of the Customs Tariff Act, 1975 (51 of 1975), the Central Government hereby appoints the Assistant Commissioner/Deputy Commissioner of Customs, Group 2B-I, in the Commissionerate of Customs (Import), Mumbai, to exercise the powers and discharge the duties of Assistant Commissioner / Deputy Commissioner of Customs (Refund), as the case may be, for the purpose of disposing of applications filed under sub-section (2) of section 9AA of the said Act, within the jurisdiction of the Commissionerate of Customs (Import), Mumbai. F.No. 525/2/94-Cus (TU) V. Kezo Under Secretary to the Govt. of India -- 1 of 1 --",
